060     * Create a new {@code ShorthandParserEventHandler}.
061     *
062     * @param knownFunctionalGroups the known functional groups
063     */

087                    entry("unsorted_fa_separator_pre_event", this::setMolecularLevel),

185    @Override
186    protected void resetParser(TreeNode node) {
187        content = null;
188        level = LipidLevel.COMPLETE_STRUCTURE;
189        adduct = null;
190        headGroup = "";
191        faList.clear();
192        currentFas.clear();
193        headgroupDecorators.clear();
194        tmp = new Dictionary();
195        acerSpecies = false;
196        heavyElement = Element.C;
197        heavyElementNumber = 0;
198    }
199
200    private String faI() {
201        return "fa" + Integer.toString(currentFas.size());
202    }

207    }

209    private void setCarbohydrateNumber(TreeNode node) {
210        int carbohydrateNum = node.getInt();
211        if (!headgroupDecorators.isEmpty() && carbohydrateNum > 0){
212            HeadgroupDecorator lastElement = headgroupDecorators.get(headgroupDecorators.size() - 1);
213            int cnt = lastElement.getCount();
214            lastElement.setCount(cnt + carbohydrateNum - 1);
215        }
216    }

218
219    private void buildLipid(TreeNode node) {
220        if (acerSpecies) {
221            faList.get(0).setNumCarbon(faList.get(0).getNumCarbon() - 2);
222        }
223        Headgroup headgroup = prepareHeadgroupAndChecks();
224
225        // add count numbers for fatty acyl chains
226        int fa_it = (faList.size() > 0 && (faList.get(0).getLipidFaBondType() == LipidFaBondType.LCB_EXCEPTION || faList.get(0).getLipidFaBondType() == LipidFaBondType.LCB_REGULAR)) ? 1 : 0;
227        for (int it = fa_it; it < faList.size(); ++it) {
228            faList.get(it).setName(faList.get(it).getName() + Integer.toString(it + 1));
229        }
230
231        LipidAdduct lipid = new LipidAdduct(assembleLipid(headgroup), adduct);
232
233        if (tmp.containsKey("num_ethers")) {
234            lipid.getLipid().getInfo().numEthers = (int) tmp.get("num_ethers");
235        }
236
237        content = lipid;
238    }
239
240    private void setSterolDefinition(TreeNode node) {
241        headGroup += " " + node.getText();
242        faList.remove(0);
243
244    }

246    private void preSphingolipid(TreeNode node) {
247        tmp.put("sl_hydroxyl", 0);
248    }

250    private void postSphingolipid(TreeNode node) {
251        if (((int) tmp.get("sl_hydroxyl")) == 0 && !headGroup.equals("Cer") && !headGroup.equals("SPB")) {
252            setLipidLevel(LipidLevel.STRUCTURE_DEFINED);
253        }
254    }

258    }

272    private void addChargeSign(TreeNode node) {
273        String sign = node.getText();
274        if (sign.equals("+")) {
275            adduct.setChargeSign(1);
276        } else {
277            adduct.setChargeSign(-1);
278        }
279        if (adduct.getCharge() == 0) adduct.setCharge(1);
280    }

302    private void setEtherNum(TreeNode node) {
303        int num_ethers = 0;
304        String ether = node.getText();
305        switch (ether) {
306            case "d":
307                num_ethers = 2;
308                break;
309            case "t":
310                num_ethers = 3;
311                break;
312            case "e":
313                num_ethers = 4;
314                break;
315            default:
316                break;
317        }
318        tmp.put("num_ethers", num_ethers);
319    }

321    private void setHeadgroupName(TreeNode node) {
322        if (headGroup.length() == 0) {
323            headGroup = node.getText();
324        }
325    }

327    private void setCarbohydrate(TreeNode node) {
328        String carbohydrate = node.getText();
329        FunctionalGroup functional_group = null;
330        try {
331            functional_group = knownFunctionalGroups.get(carbohydrate);
332        } catch (Exception e) {
333            throw new LipidParsingException("Carbohydrate '" + carbohydrate + "' unknown");
334        }
335
336        functional_group.getElements().put(Element.O, functional_group.getElements().get(Element.O) - 1);
337        if (tmp.containsKey("func_group_head") && ((int) tmp.get("func_group_head") == 1)) {
338            headgroupDecorators.add((HeadgroupDecorator) functional_group);
339        } else {
340            if (!currentFas.peekLast().getFunctionalGroupsInternal().containsKey(carbohydrate)) {
341                currentFas.peekLast().getFunctionalGroupsInternal().put(carbohydrate, new ArrayList<>());
342            }
343            currentFas.peekLast().getFunctionalGroupsInternal().get(carbohydrate).add(functional_group);
344        }
345    }

362        newFattyAcylChain(node);
363        currentFas.getLast().setName("LCB");
364        ((FattyAcid)currentFas.getLast()).setType(LipidFaBondType.LCB_REGULAR);

367    private void newFattyAcylChain(TreeNode node) {
368        currentFas.add(new FattyAcid("FA", knownFunctionalGroups));
369        tmp.put(faI(), new Dictionary());
370    }
371
372    private void addFattyAcylChain(TreeNode node) {
373        String fg_i = "fa" + Integer.toString(currentFas.size() - 2);
374        String special_type = "";
375        if (currentFas.size() >= 2 && tmp.containsKey(fg_i) && ((Dictionary) tmp.get(fg_i)).containsKey("fg_name")) {
376            String fg_name = (String) ((Dictionary) tmp.get(fg_i)).get("fg_name");
377            if (SPECIAL_TYPES.contains(fg_name)) {
378                special_type = fg_name;
379            }
380        }
381
382        String fa_i = faI();
383        if (currentFas.peekLast().getDoubleBonds().getNumDoubleBonds() != (int) ((Dictionary) tmp.get(fa_i)).get("db_count")) {
384            throw new LipidException("Double bond count does not match with number of double bond positions");
385        } else if (currentFas.peekLast().getDoubleBonds().getNumDoubleBonds() > 0 && currentFas.peekLast().getDoubleBonds().getDoubleBondPositions().isEmpty()) {
386            setLipidLevel(LipidLevel.SN_POSITION);
387        }
388        tmp.remove(fa_i);
389
390        FattyAcid fa = (FattyAcid) currentFas.pollLast();
391        if (special_type.length() > 0) {
392            fa.setName(special_type);
393            if (!currentFas.peekLast().getFunctionalGroupsInternal().containsKey(special_type)) {
394                currentFas.peekLast().getFunctionalGroupsInternal().put(special_type, new ArrayList<>());
395            }
396            currentFas.peekLast().getFunctionalGroupsInternal().get(special_type).add(fa);
397        } else {
398            faList.add(fa);
399        }
400    }

416    private void setDoubleBondInformation(TreeNode node) {
417        String fa_i = faI();
418        ((Dictionary) tmp.get(fa_i)).put("db_position", 0);
419        ((Dictionary) tmp.get(fa_i)).put("db_cistrans", "");
420    }
421
422    private void addDoubleBondInformation(TreeNode node) {
423        String fa_i = faI();
424        Dictionary d = (Dictionary) tmp.get(fa_i);
425        int pos = (int) d.get("db_position");
426        String cistrans = (String) d.get("db_cistrans");
427
428        if (cistrans.equals("")) {
429            setLipidLevel(LipidLevel.STRUCTURE_DEFINED);
430        }
431
432        d.remove("db_position");
433        d.remove("db_cistrans");
434        currentFas.peekLast().getDoubleBonds().getDoubleBondPositions().put(pos, cistrans);
435    }

438        ((Dictionary) tmp.get(faI())).put("db_cistrans", node.getText());
439    }

441    private void setEtherType(TreeNode node) {
442        String ether_type = node.getText();
443        if (ether_type.equals("O-")) {
444            ((FattyAcid) currentFas.peekLast()).setLipidFaBondType(LipidFaBondType.ETHER_PLASMANYL);
445        } else if (ether_type.equals("P-")) {
446            ((FattyAcid) currentFas.peekLast()).setLipidFaBondType(LipidFaBondType.ETHER_PLASMENYL);
447        }
448    }

450    private void setFunctionalGroup(TreeNode node) {
451        String fa_i = faI();
452        Dictionary gd = (Dictionary) tmp.get(fa_i);
453        gd.put("fg_pos", -1);
454        gd.put("fg_name", "0");
455        gd.put("fg_cnt", 1);
456        gd.put("fg_stereo", "");
457        gd.put("fg_ring_stereo", "");
458    }

461    private void addDiHydroxyl(TreeNode node) {
462        if (!FattyAcid.LCB_STATES.contains(((FattyAcid)currentFas.getLast()).getLipidFaBondType())) return;
463        int num_h = 1;
464
465        if (FattyAcid.fgExceptions.contains(headGroup) && !headgroupDecorators.isEmpty()) {
466            num_h -= 1;
467        }
468
469        FunctionalGroup functional_group = knownFunctionalGroups.get("OH");
470        functional_group.setCount(num_h);
471        if (!currentFa.getFunctionalGroupsInternal().containsKey("OH")) {
472            currentFa.getFunctionalGroupsInternal().put("OH", new ArrayList<>());
473        }
474        currentFa.getFunctionalGroupsInternal().get("OH").add(functional_group);
475    }
476    
477
478    private void addFunctionalGroup(TreeNode node) {
479        Dictionary gd = (Dictionary) tmp.get(faI());
480        String fg_name = (String) gd.get("fg_name");
481
482        if (SPECIAL_TYPES.contains(fg_name) || fg_name.equals("cy")) {
483            return;
484        }
485
486        int fg_pos = (int) gd.get("fg_pos");
487        int fg_cnt = (int) gd.get("fg_cnt");
488        String fg_stereo = (String) gd.get("fg_stereo");
489        String fg_ring_stereo = (String) gd.get("fg_ring_stereo");
490
491        if (fg_pos == -1) {
492            setLipidLevel(LipidLevel.STRUCTURE_DEFINED);
493        }
494        if (fg_cnt <= 0) return;
495
496        FunctionalGroup functional_group = null;
497        try {
498            functional_group = knownFunctionalGroups.get(fg_name);
499        } catch (Exception e) {
500            throw new LipidParsingException("'" + fg_name + "' unknown");
501        }
502
503        functional_group.setPosition(fg_pos);
504        functional_group.setCount(fg_cnt);
505        functional_group.setStereochemistry(fg_stereo);
506        functional_group.setRingStereo(fg_ring_stereo);
507
508        gd.remove("fg_pos");
509        gd.remove("fg_name");
510        gd.remove("fg_cnt");
511        gd.remove("fg_stereo");
512
513        if (!currentFas.peekLast().getFunctionalGroupsInternal().containsKey(fg_name)) {
514            currentFas.peekLast().getFunctionalGroupsInternal().put(fg_name, new ArrayList<>());
515        }
516        currentFas.peekLast().getFunctionalGroupsInternal().get(fg_name).add(functional_group);
517    }

540    private void setCycle(TreeNode node) {
541        ((Dictionary) tmp.get(faI())).put("fg_name", "cy");
542        currentFas.add(new Cycle(0, knownFunctionalGroups));

548
549    private void addCycle(TreeNode node) {
550        String fa_i = faI();
551        GenericList cycle_elements = (GenericList) ((Dictionary) tmp.get(fa_i)).get("cycle_elements");
552        Cycle cycle = (Cycle) currentFas.pollLast();
553        for (int i = 0; i < cycle_elements.size(); ++i) {
554            cycle.getBridgeChain().add((Element) cycle_elements.get(i));
555        }
556        ((Dictionary) tmp.get(fa_i)).remove("cycle_elements");
557
558        if (cycle.getStart() > -1 && cycle.getEnd() > -1 && cycle.getEnd() - cycle.getStart() + 1 + cycle.getBridgeChain().size() < cycle.getCycle()) {
559            throw new ConstraintViolationException("Cycle length '" + Integer.toString(cycle.getCycle()) + "' does not match with cycle description.");
560        }
561        if (!currentFas.peekLast().getFunctionalGroupsInternal().containsKey("cy")) {
562            currentFas.peekLast().getFunctionalGroupsInternal().put("cy", new ArrayList<>());
563        }
564        currentFas.peekLast().getFunctionalGroupsInternal().get("cy").add(cycle);
565    }

587    private void checkCycleDbPositions(TreeNode node) {
588        if (((Cycle) currentFas.peekLast()).getDoubleBonds().getNumDoubleBonds() != (int) ((Dictionary) tmp.get(faI())).get("cycle_db")) {
589            throw new LipidException("Double bond number in cycle does not correspond to number of double bond positions.");
590        }
591    }

604    private void addCycleElement(TreeNode node) {
605        String element = node.getText();
606
607        if (!Elements.ELEMENT_POSITIONS.containsKey(element)) {
608            throw new LipidParsingException("Element '" + element + "' unknown");
609        }
610
611        ((GenericList) ((Dictionary) tmp.get(faI())).get("cycle_elements")).add(Elements.ELEMENT_POSITIONS.get(element));
612    }

614    private void setAcylLinkage(TreeNode node) {
615        ((Dictionary) tmp.get(faI())).put("fg_name", "acyl");
616        currentFas.add(new AcylAlkylGroup((FattyAcid) null, knownFunctionalGroups));
617        tmp.put(faI(), new Dictionary());
618        ((Dictionary) tmp.get(faI())).put("linkage_pos", -1);
619    }

621    private void addAcylLinkage(TreeNode node) {
622        boolean linkage_type = (int) ((Dictionary) tmp.get(faI())).get("linkage_type") == 1;
623        int linkage_pos = (int) ((Dictionary) tmp.get(faI())).get("linkage_pos");
624
625        tmp.remove(faI());
626        AcylAlkylGroup acyl = (AcylAlkylGroup) currentFas.pollLast();
627
628        acyl.setPosition(linkage_pos);
629        acyl.setNitrogenBond(linkage_type);
630        if (linkage_pos == -1) {
631            setLipidLevel(LipidLevel.STRUCTURE_DEFINED);
632        }
633
634        if (!currentFas.peekLast().getFunctionalGroupsInternal().containsKey("acyl")) {
635            currentFas.peekLast().getFunctionalGroupsInternal().put("acyl", new ArrayList<FunctionalGroup>());
636        }
637        currentFas.peekLast().getFunctionalGroupsInternal().get("acyl").add(acyl);
638    }

724    private void addPlSpeciesData(TreeNode node) {
725        setLipidLevel(LipidLevel.SPECIES);
726        HeadgroupDecorator hgd = new HeadgroupDecorator("", knownFunctionalGroups);
727        hgd.getElements().put(Element.O, hgd.getElements().get(Element.O) + 1);
728        hgd.getElements().put(Element.H, hgd.getElements().get(Element.H) - 1);
729        headgroupDecorators.add(hgd);
730    }

740    private void setAcer(TreeNode node) {
741        headGroup = "ACer";
742        HeadgroupDecorator hgd = new HeadgroupDecorator("decorator_acyl", -1, 1, null, true, knownFunctionalGroups);
743        hgd.getFunctionalGroupsInternal().put("decorator_acyl", new ArrayList<>());
744        hgd.getFunctionalGroupsInternal().get("decorator_acyl").add(faList.get(faList.size() - 1));
745        faList.remove(faList.size() - 1);
746        headgroupDecorators.add(hgd);
747    }
